HEADWORD: androgen
<hw>androgen</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a hormone, such as
testosterone or androsterone, that promotes development and maintenance
of typical male sexual characteristics. They are mostly produced in the
testes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

